  "informal_statement": "If two finite sets are disjoint, the number of elements in their union equals the sum of their individual sizes.",
  "informal_proof_idea": "Directly `Finset.card_union_eq_card_add_card` (an iff between the equality and disjointness), taking the `mpr` direction.",
  "formal_statement_pp": "theorem disjoint_union_card' (s t : Finset ℕ) (h : Disjoint s t) : (s ∪ t).card = s.card + t.card",
